01:45:33.540 --> 01:45:37.620
or to have paper genocide
happen because the census is

01:45:37.620 --> 01:45:39.280
in real danger, as I
think you all know.

01:45:39.280 --> 01:45:40.580
So I wanted to mention that.

01:45:40.580 --> 01:45:43.160
Professor Vinson,
congratulations

01:45:43.160 --> 01:45:45.470
at William &amp; Mary has its
