01:55:50.310 --> 01:55:55.510
And I'd like to close

01:55:55.510 --> 01:55:59.930
by reflecting myself
on the question.

01:55:59.930 --> 01:56:02.940
What is the most significant
thing you would like others

01:56:02.940 --> 01:56:06.250
