to surface as an opening

01:56:27.190 --> 01:56:32.510
of moral space for
a conversation

01:56:32.510 --> 01:56:36.870
about many kinds of repair.

01:56:36.870 --> 01:56:49.870
Soul repair, material
reparations, and just a thought

01:56:49.870 --> 01:56:54.990
about what it means
to be an American

01:56:54.990 --> 01:57:01.800
and how we became Americans.

01:57:01.800 --> 01:57:10.740
So this space is open now,
and we're going to do our best

01:57:10.740 --> 01:57:15.490
to hold it open through 2019.

01:57:15.490 --> 01:57:17.770
Please join us.

01:57:17.770 --> 01:57:19.570
Thank you.

